      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUDDY BONUS (2) has been in the minors the last two, the latest showing strong pace early but gathered in and finished a 1.3 lengths second over 350m this track in 20.02. Top chance in this line up. NANNY'S BOY (3) ran good time (17.06) when second last start over 300m at Casino, the second placing in a row. Can turn it around this time. OPHIDIAN (7) continues to race in super honest form hitting the frame at 11 of 16 career runs, winning two back before finishing third last time (20.12) over 350m at this track. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. KINGSBRAE REX (4) did a good job to finish third last time out over 350m at this track (20.15) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
